Quin, Appellant, v. Winter, Respondent. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 6,1890.)

Argued before Bookstaver, P. J., and Bischoff, J.

No opinion. Motion for leave to appeal to court of appeals denied, with $10 costs. For former reports, see 4 N. Y. Supp. 865; 7 N. Y. Supp. 755.
